BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:RVl2d5hjrzijt7m_U50AJ
SUMMARY:Intro to Improv Eastside - Issaquah SUNDAYS
DTSTAMP:20260307T235615Z
DTSTART:20260308T110000Z
DESCRIPTION:Discover improv in Issaquah. Build confidence\\\, meet new peop
	le\\\, and learn to create stories through fun\\\, supportive games and sc
	ene work.\\n\\n\\n\\nLooking for a fun\\\, fresh way to connect with other
	s\\\, spark creativity\\\, and step out of the everyday routine? Welcome t
	o Intro to Improv at Unexpected Productions Improv School Eastside in Issa
	quah. Whether you are a working professional hoping to improve communicati
	on\\\, a creative soul searching for a new outlet\\\, or someone simply wa
	nting more laughter and community in your week\\\, this class is the perfe
	ct place to begin. \\nIn this beginner-friendly course\\\, you will learn 
	the foundational skills of improvisation: active listening\\\, collaborati
	on\\\, spontaneity\\\, and using your own life experiences to create hones
	t\\\, engaging scenes and stories. Improv is not about being funny\\\, it 
	is about being present\\\, supportive\\\, and open. And yes\\\, along the 
	way\\\, you will laugh more than you have in ages. \\nOur community values
	 connection and growth\\\, and this class is built on those principles. Yo
	u will work in a supportive group where the guiding philosophy is simple: 
	When your scene partner looks good\\\, you look good. Together\\\, we buil
	d trust\\\, confidence\\\, and creativity\\\, one scene at a time. \\n\\nU
	nder the guidance of our experienced faculty\\\, you will learn to:\\nBe a
	 better listener\\nConquer fears and build confidence\\nSpark creativity\\
	nMeet new people and make real connections\\nBecome a better problem solve
	r\\nSay yes more in your life\\nStep out of your comfort zone\\nImprove pu
	blic speaking\\nFail easier (and laugh about it)\\nDiscover more about you
	rself\\nHave an absolute blast\\n\\nThis class includes lots of laughter\\
	\, lots of stage time\\\, and zero pressure. Every student begins here. No
	 experience needed. Just bring curiosity and a willingness to try somethin
	g new. \\nUnexpected Productions Improv School is thrilled to bring our ne
	west Eastside improv classes to Issaquah\\\, serving the communities of th
	e Sammamish Plateau\\\, East Renton\\\, Bellevue\\\, Snoqualmie Valley\\\,
	 and beyond. \\nClass Details\\nDates: Sundays for eight (8) weeks\\\, fro
	m March 8 to May 3\\\, (No class on April 5th) \\nTime: 11:00 AM to 1:00pm
	 \\nLocation: Improv School Eastside Issaquah \\n1315 NW Mall Street\\\, S
	uite 4 Issaquah\\\, WA 98027 (next to the Gaslamp Bar & Grill) \\nMaximum 
	students: 16 \\nAges: 18 plus \\nCost: $320 \\nPrerequisite: None \\nNote:
	 Attendance at the first session is mandatory\\\, as it sets the tone and 
	foundation for the entire quarter. If you know you will miss the first cla
	ss\\\, please register for a future session. \\nWhat students say\\n“You a
	re learning more about improv\\\, more about yourself\\\, making interesti
	ng friends\\\, while you are learning and stretching in ways that will mak
	e life better both at work and socially\\\, yet everyone is smiling so har
	d your face hurts. How many stars is that worth?” \\nJonathan A.\\\, 5 Sta
	rs on Yelp \\nCancellation policy\\nThere are no refunds.\n\nhttps://www.u
	nexpectedproductions.org/event/intro-to-improv-eastside-issaquah-sundays/\
	n\nFrom Unexpected Productions
URL:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/intro-to-improv-eastside-is
	saquah-sundays/
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions Improv School ISSAQUAH/EASTSIDE\\\, 1315 NW
	 Mall Street\\\, Suite 4\\\, Issaquah\\\, WA\\\, 98108\\\, United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:unexpected-productions
CATEGORIES:Unexpected Productions
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:B-ZpcoJvaR4ODBlDhOab8
SUMMARY:Show Your Game: An Improvised Game Show
DTSTAMP:20260307T235615Z
DTSTART:20260308T193000Z
DESCRIPTION:Ever wonder what secret skills your neighbors are hiding? That 
	quiet person next to you on the bus might be a brain surgeon\\\, a barbecu
	e champion\\\, or the only parent in town who can get their toddler to nap
	 on time. Show Your Game is here to celebrate those everyday experts and u
	nexpected talents! \\nEach night\\\, a hilarious mix of improvisers and br
	ave audience members go head-to-head\\\, diving deep into the worlds of tw
	o surprising experts. They’ll tackle quirky questions and wild challenges\
	\\, each crafted by the experts themselves to test just how much our conte
	stants really know. \\nLove the clever chaos of QI\\\, the unpredictable t
	wists of Game Changer\\\, or the absurd fun of Taskmaster? Then this is yo
	ur kind of show. \\nSo\\\, when it’s your turn to step into someone else’s
	 world… are you ready to Show Your Game?\n\nhttps://www.unexpectedproducti
	ons.org/event/show-your-game-an-improvised-game-show-3/2026-03-08/\n\nFrom
	 Unexpected Productions
URL:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/show-your-game-an-improvise
	d-game-show-3/2026-03-08/
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions\\\, 1428 Post Alley at the Gum Wall in Pike
	 Place Market\\\, Seattle\\\, WA\\\, 98101\\\, United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:unexpected-productions
CATEGORIES:Unexpected Productions
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
